com.xilinx.rapidwright.rwroute

Class TimingAndWirelengthReport

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.rwroute.TimingAndWirelengthReport

  • public class TimingAndWirelengthReport
extends Object
    An example to report the critical path delay and total wirelength of a routed design. It is able to reproduce the same statistics as a RWRoute Object reports after routing a design.
